This paper deals with the theoretical analysis of reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). It also involves decision-making and optimization in multi-agent systems (cs.MA), as well as game theory (cs.GT) and control systems (cs.SY).
